	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseWeaponNeolithic">
		<defName>TSOA_AnimaBow</defName>
		<label>anima bow</label>
		<description>A bow carved from anima tree bark. It imparts its arrows with psychic energy that is released on impact, causing a small psychic scream that reduces humans' moods and makes wild animals turn manhunter.</description>
